{"parentUuid":"df4c5895-0694-47db-b7b2-42b134cda815","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/matianjun/Dropbox/code/hyperliquid_analyse","sessionId":"cbae4261-7c32-4a6f-ae93-2b9ca7e84858","version":"2.1.39","gitBranch":"master","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"请你阅读 @commands/ml_commands_12h.py 里面generate_weights_12h的逻辑。核心逻辑在 @ranker_model/regression_portfolio_optimizer_generator_4h.py 和 @ranker_model/regression_portfolio_optimizer.py \n请你理解逻辑，然后列出来哪些地方应该优化一下运行速度，现在跑一次weights 生成太久了。\n这里是一些实现思路，给你参考\n单币权重约束 (Weight Bounds)：默认每个币的持仓比例被限制在 [-0.1, 0.1] 之间，防止单币暴雷（黑天鹅）导致整体净值重挫。总杠杆约束 (Leverage Limit)：$\\sum |w_i| \\le 5$。多头仓位绝对值 + 空头仓位绝对值之和不能超过 5 倍杠杆。贝塔中性约束 (Beta Neutrality)：$\\sum (w_i \\cdot \\beta_i) = 0$。强制要求多头和空头在波动率（脾气）上互相抵消，彻底剥离大盘系统性风险。动态净敞口约束 (Dynamic Net Exposure)：引入了外部另类数据（Fear & Greed Index）。极度贪婪时，顺势放宽多头敞口（最高 30% 净多头）；极度恐慌时，放宽空头敞口。$\\sum w_i \\in [min\\_net, max\\_net]$。"},"uuid":"788f87d1-1b55-4c0c-b43a-9d1e787b4dd9","timestamp":"2026-02-23T02:23:20.679Z","thinkingMetadata":{"maxThinkingTokens":31999},"todos":[],"permissionMode":"bypassPermissions"}
